        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, peel and finely dice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>parsley & dill</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1664293606446-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1664293606446-x400.jpg",
