            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>diced shallot</strong> and <strong>chopped herbs </strong>in a large bowl with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> salmon flakes</strong>, <strong>ground cumin </strong>and <strong>ground turmeric</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>salmon mixture</strong></p>",
